**Findings**

1. `F001`
Severity: `HIGH`
Category: `code-bug`
Type: `behavior_change`
Before-behavior: 当前组件的焦点态是内部 `ref`，由 `node:click` / `clearFocus` / `focusPeer` 驱动，未声明 `focusedNodeId` prop。
After-behavior: 计划把焦点源改成 `props.focusedNodeId`，并要求测试用 `wrapper.setProps({ focusedNodeId: ... })` 驱动。
Evidence: [ConceptMapPanel.vue:69](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L69), [ConceptMapPanel.vue:87](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L87), [ConceptMapPanel.vue:190](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L190), [phase2.5-plan.md:46](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L46), [phase2.5-plan.md:75](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L75), [phase2.5-plan.md:322](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L322), [phase2.5-plan.md:352](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L352)
Impact: 按计划原样实施，功能和测试都对不上当前代码；若强行新增 prop，又把已上线的内部焦点机制改成外部接口，属于未请求的接口漂移。
Repair hypothesis: 保持焦点源为内部 `focusedNodeId`，新增逻辑改为依赖/监听该 `ref`，测试从现有 `graph` 事件入口或已暴露实例状态驱动。

2. `F002`
Severity: `HIGH`
Category: `code-bug`
Type: `behavior_change`
Before-behavior: 当前 `defineExpose` 暴露 `crossModuleBadges`、`crossModulePeers`、`focusedNodeId`、`clearFocus`；现有 Phase 2 测试已依赖这组暴露接口验证焦点交互。
After-behavior: 计划的三处 `defineExpose` 示例都把 `focusedNodeId` / `clearFocus` 从暴露集合中删掉，只保留新增字段。
Evidence: [ConceptMapPanel.vue:289](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L289), [ConceptMapPanel.test.js:208](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/__tests__/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.test.js#L208), [ConceptMapPanel.test.js:229](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/__tests__/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.test.js#L229), [phase2.5-plan.md:102](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L102), [phase2.5-plan.md:360](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L360), [phase2.5-plan.md:603](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L603)
Impact: 会直接破坏现有已上线/已验证的测试契约，属于回归风险，不满足“Phase 2 frozen”前提。
Repair hypothesis: `defineExpose` 只能增量扩展，必须保留 `focusedNodeId` 和 `clearFocus`。

3. `F003`
Severity: `MEDIUM`
Category: `code-bug`
Type: `defect_fix`
Before-behavior: 当前 `buildG6Data()` 先按可见节点过滤边，再在过滤后的数组上生成 `edge-${i}`。
After-behavior: 计划里的 `relatedEdgeIds` 和 `stateMap` 都按 `props.edges` 原始索引生成 `edge-${i}`，并声称“与 buildG6Data 严格一致”。
